## Step 4: Asset licensing (non-negotiable)

- All assets must be **CC0 or permissive** (compatible with commercial Steam release)
- Every new asset or pack must have an entry in `assets/ATTRIBUTION.md`
- Source packs go in `.cursor/human_provided/` with their original license files
- After adding assets, run: `python tools/validate_assets.py --check-attribution`

