## Step 6: Before/after workflow for visual changes

1. Capture baseline screenshots if not already done:
   ```
   python tools/capture_screenshots.py --scenario base_overview --seed 3 --out docs/screenshots/before_<feature> --size 1920x1080 --ticks 0
   ```
2. Make the change.
3. Capture after screenshots to the same structure but `after_<feature>`.
4. Run the compare gallery if available:
   ```
   python tools/build_gallery.py --shots docs/screenshots/after_<feature> --refs docs/screenshots/before_<feature> --out docs/art/compare_gallery.html
   ```
5. Run QA gate:
   ```
   python tools/qa_smoke.py --quick
   ```

