## Step 8: Common mistakes to avoid

| Mistake | Correct behaviour |
|---|---|
| Waiting for approval before implementing | Just implement. If PM assigned it, do it. |
| Using `ApplyPatch` repeatedly when it fails | Switch to `StrReplace` immediately |
| Changing footprint/anchor sizes on buildings | Forbidden — breaks placement collision |
| Using `time.time()` or unseeded `random` in sprite generation | Use `zlib.crc32` + tile/entity coords as seed |
| Creating per-frame Surface allocations | Cache all generated surfaces in a dict |
| Editing `game/ui/` files | That is Agent 08's domain — coordinate or hand off |
| Reporting "done" without running `qa_smoke --quick` | Always run and include exit code in log |
| Writing essays in your log | Use bullets and file:line references |

